e":118,"score":-115,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"講緊你老母定你自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef1aae485de49743811a742e555afdd9daebe37","tid":2393542,"uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92157faad9d4e53e282f31a298ae93cd6b36b8bc","tid":2393542,"uid":78769,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"前南斯拉夫發生嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本種族清洗<br />\n<br />\n但支那國已經養到咁大，太難有效對付"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yubx6vm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYubx6vm.jpg&h=560af3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新疆「再教育營」：新文件揭穆斯林如何因蓄須、蒙面和上網被拘留<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月21日<br />\n<br />\n圖像來源，UHRP<br />\n<br />\nBBC新獲得了一批洩露文件，它們似乎對中國如何決定新疆地區被拘押穆斯林的命運，提供了迄今為止最有力的洞察。<br />\n<br />\n該文件包含3000多名來自中國西部邊陲的新疆地區公民的個人信息，詳細羅列了他們日常生活中最私密的細節。<br />\n<br />\n這份137頁的表格面面俱到地記錄了人們禮拜的頻率、著裝、聯繫對象以及家人的表現。<br />\n<br />\n中國當局否認有任何不當行為，稱行動旨在打擊恐怖主義和宗教極端主義。<br />\n<br />\n這批文件據稱是冒著巨大的個人風險而得以流出。它們與去年洩露的一批來自新疆境內的高度敏感材料屬於同一來源。<br />\n<br />\n國際新疆問題權威學者、華盛頓共產主義受害者紀念基金會（Victims of Communism Memorial Foundation）高級研究員鄭國恩（Adrian Zenz）博士認為，此批洩密文件是真實的。<br />\n<br />\n「這份重要文件提供了迄今為止我所見過的最有力的證據，表明北京在對傳統的宗教信仰進行積極打壓和懲罰，」他說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51569535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51569535&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=99cda85d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51569535&h=66e5d637\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51569535</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8013227/Chinese-authorities-compile-intimate-data-Uighur-Muslim-population.html?ito=social-twitter_mailonline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8013227%2FChinese-authorities-compile-intimate-data-Uighur-Muslim-population.html%3Fito%3Dsocial-twitter_mailonline&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=6778e268\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8013227/Chinese-authorities-compile-intimate-data-Uighur-Muslim-population.html?ito=social-twitter_mailonline</a>"},{"pid":"a36d98ea08981743cf6222bc84e0eb9094e72be2","tid":2393542,"uid":78873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"都幾肯定熱巴條賣維女一定比漢人屌過無數次"},{"pid":"e6b5658ae31490850aa2e2109d23df10984a1c8a","tid":2393542,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:32:21.000Z","msg":"左膠睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198692c35c71eb5c4beb36b2f69eb03c28eb5474","tid":2393542,"uid":37333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70039064f9ea97e7741d76bc242d0254d9f29f35","tid":2393542,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65955d421f0c1168734d4b8f25104451ce5de63","tid":2393542,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好癲"},{"pid":"715e8c500ba1de54fe74d6a6976d4c0586b1c86b","tid":2393542,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:49:05.000Z","msg":"